      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"2. BOURNE FRANKY latest effort finished 3rd on April 9 over 400m at this track behind Compton Shelly beaten 11 lengths (23.72) in a Other. With a clean break looks hard to beat. 1. WILD STAR had the drop on the lead and went on to be beaten 2.5 lengths into third (23.44) at this track in a Grade 2/3/4 over 400m. Boasts a strong record from this draw with four wins and three minor placings from nine starts. Leading player again. 8. OREGON CALDWELL continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at his last four runs. Last start finished 2nd over 512m at this track beaten 6 lengths (29.83) behind Kia Keeping in a Other on April 9. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Overdue and is among the main hopes. 6. CROWIE UNLEASHED placed last time and is worth some thought.\",\"runners\":[2,1,8,6],\"exclusive\":false}",
